## 📌 Overview

**My CV** is a sleek, animated portfolio app that replaces the traditional paper resume with an immersive mobile experience. Every section — from skills to experience — is thoughtfully designed to make a lasting impression on anyone who views it.

---

## ✨ Features

### 🎨 Dynamic Theme Switching
Three hand-crafted themes to match any mood or occasion:

| Theme | Color Palette |
|:---|:---|
| 🔵 Classic | Indigo / Blue |
| 🟣 Modern | Purple / Pink |
| 🟢 Creative | Teal / Green |

### 🖼️ Interactive Profile Gallery
- Swipe through multiple profile images with gesture support
- Tap-to-zoom popup for a full-screen closer look

### 💼 Comprehensive Career Overview
- **About Me** — Personal introduction paired with dynamic skill chips
- **Skills** — Visual progress bars showing proficiency in AI, Flutter, Web & more
- **Experience Timeline** — Vertical timeline of professional milestones
- **Projects & Education** — Key deliverables and academic background

### 📡 Quick Connectivity
- Animated social media shortcut buttons
- Tap-to-contact cards for instant communication

### 🖥️ Modern UI / UX
- Glassmorphism-inspired card elements
- Smooth animated containers and page transitions
- Built on Material Design with fully custom styling

---

